quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  40,34,"GooŇč…óii Yuusufu ardanii on e …ďannganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraani e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, mbiu…óon: "Allah nultataa Nulaa…óo goo, …ďaawo makko". Ko non majjinirta kala gon…óo fantinoowo cikkitii…óo."
  40,35,"∆Āeen wee√Īiroo…ďe e aayeeje Allah …óen ko aldaa e hujja ar…óo …ďe, [kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen. Ko wano non Allah notirta e …ďernde kala mawnintinii…óo dundarankeejo."
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: " eey ma yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo …óate …óen."
  40,37,"…óate kammuuji …óin, mi ∆īeewoya Dewetee…óo Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo penoowo". Ko wano non Fir'awna du…óiranaa, golle makko bon…óe …óen; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wonaa e hayrere."
  40,38,"[Gorko] gooŇč…óin…óo on wi'i: "eey mon yo yim…ďe am, njokkee kam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol."
  40,39,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe am, nganndee …óam nguurndam aduna, ko ndakamme-hun tun, ko La'akara on woni, galle √Īii…ďal …óen."
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yo…ďitetaake, si wonaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi mo∆ī∆īere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gooŇč…óin…óo, …ďeen …óoon naatay Aljanna, …ďe arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore."